<item>
            <title>[LU-5586] Duplicate &quot;xattr&quot; from sbi_flags under procfs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5586</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[root@mercury tests]# cat /proc/fs/lustre/llite/*/sbi_flags 
checksum flock xattr acl lru_resize 64bit_hash agl verbose layout xattr 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The problem is in the definition of LL_SBI_FLAGS in llite_internal.h where two &quot;xattr&quot; coexist.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;#define LL_SBI_FLAGS {  \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;nolck&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,        \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;checksum&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,     \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;flock&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,        \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;xattr&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,        \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;acl&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,          \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;???&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,          \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;rmt_client&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,   \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;mds_capa&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,     \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;oss_capa&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,     \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;flock&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,        \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;lru_resize&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,   \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;lazy_statfs&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,  \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;som&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,          \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;32bit_api&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,    \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;64bit_hash&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,   \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;agl&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,          \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;verbose&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,      \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;layout&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,       \
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;user_fid2path&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,\
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;xattr&quot;&lt;/span&gt;,        \
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first one should be changed to &quot;user_xattr&quot; and the latter one should be &quot;xattr_cache&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
